{"tid":729893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普曾表明要推翻「墮胎合法化」判決","createTime":"2018-07-05T03:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T11:05:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ebab4cc5b28e141d56db1c12d755a701ef5dcdc9","tid":729893,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/1878496/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Farticle%2Fid%2F1878496%2F&d=rsDJBa8lbVk3udcJb1DQE2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=0d3109b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/1878496/</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年6月29日<br />\n<br />\n墮胎權恐遭新官推翻<br />\n<br />\n<strong>肯尼迪擔任大法官期間一直捍衞墮胎權，支持墮胎權的組織擔心，特朗普將趁肯尼迪退休的良機兌現承諾，推翻數十年前美國墮胎合法化的最高法院裁決。</strong><br />\n<br />\n1973年美國最高法院對「羅訴韋德案」（Roe v Wade）作出判決，墮胎在大多數州變為合法，但墮胎合法與否的爭議45年來從未停止，<strong>特朗普前年競選總統時，表明一旦當選將有機會委任2至3名大法官，從而推翻「羅訴韋德案」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n支持墮胎權的組織形容，肯尼迪退休對女性生育自由構成可怕而即時的危險。大法官繼任人會從白宮25人候選名單中挑選，該名單正是由一個反墮胎的保守法律組織協助制訂。位列名單的聯邦第十一巡迴上訴法院法官普賴爾（William Pryor）曾稱，「羅訴韋德案」是憲法史上令人最憎惡的事，指當年裁決導致數以百萬計無辜胎兒被「屠殺」。"},{"pid":"2ed297655d828dc03ce7c6d73785703e3c9597a4","tid":729893,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"美國副總統Pence亦曾表示:  預計他們政府的任期內, 墮胎將不再合法<br />\n<a href=\"http://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/375852-pence-says-abortion-will-end-in-us-in-our-time\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fpolicy%2Fhealthcare%2F375852-pence-says-abortion-will-end-in-us-in-our-time&d=rsDJBa8lbVk3udcJb1DQE2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=195bc9d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://thehill.com/policy/healthcare/375852-pence-says-abortion-will-end-in-us-in-our-time</a>"},{"pid":"352adca49ef79f00e8fa67c12dfc3b59a6a9a789","tid":729893,"uid":83097,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"得班終日無所事事靠食大麻同唔帶套扑野渡日既whinny liberals先會支持無條件無限制墮胎"},{"pid":"d90a27528598d031c148d36cde0daf8e1b2a5639","tid":729893,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2b985cbc82bdd3b82ee60d9752d1d6b597abca","tid":729893,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"幫強姦犯養仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8b29195e744f84ccfa98c1f09eec9016f82173","tid":729893,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"352adca49ef79f00e8fa67c12dfc3b59a6a9a789","tid":729893,"uid":83097,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"得班終日無所事事靠食大麻同唔帶套扑野渡日既whinny liberals先會支持無條件無限制墮胎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔鍾意帶套扑野?"},{"pid":"8393fef890dfd9442599d9328fdf6061fc97c12a","tid":729893,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a8b29195e744f84ccfa98c1f09eec9016f82173","tid":729893,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"352adca49ef79f00e8fa67c12dfc3b59a6a9a789","tid":729893,"uid":83097,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:29:18.000Z","msg":"得班終日無所事事靠食大麻同唔帶套扑野渡日既whinny liberals先會支持無條件無限制墮胎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔鍾意帶套扑野?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"為咗唔戴套殺人？"},{"pid":"f833144cf2db6815490a446f091338b774af9c11","tid":729893,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a8b29195e744f84ccfa98c1f0